oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Young fawns in action
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: A black and white action photograph (1/1000 sec.) of young fawns hopping. Two fawns are in focus, and three more are in the background. They appear to be playing in a wire enclosed area.
